          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The Corvette leading the field during cautions will be a Torch Red Z51 with a spoiler and ground effects package as well as Carbon Flash exterior accents and optional GT2 bucket seats. As expected from a pace car, this Corvette will wear a unique Indy 500 livery, but Chevrolet has not indicated if it will offer a replica package for customers. "
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "GM president Mark Reuss will act as the ceremonial pace car driver leading the field of racecars to the green flag, and he had this to say:"
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "blockquote",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "“It’s truly an honor to have the opportunity to be behind the wheel of the mid-engine Corvette Pace Car at such a historic race as the Indy 500. The 2020 Corvette Stingray is the result of a close collaboration between the Corvette Racing and production engineering teams, setting a new benchmark for supercars around the world.”"
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Interestingly, the C8 Corvette won't be the first mid-engine car to pace the "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            4
          ],
          1,
          "Indy 500"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", though, as that honor goes to the "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            5
          ],
          1,
          "Pontiac Fiero"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " in 1984. In addition to the 17 Corvettes that have paced Indy, a Chevrolet has acted as pace car 31 times – more than any other automaker – with the first being the Fleetmaster convertible back in 1948."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
